item.title: CVE-2019-7961|2024-08-04T21:02:19.398Z -- adobe -- adobe%20prelude%20cc
item.description: Adobe Prelude CC versions 8.1 and earlier have an insecure library loading (dll hijacking) vulnerability. Successful exploitation could lead to arbitrary code execution.
